        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2819709437" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1928584058888228036">An alternative blip in history, it melds a terrifying possibility with the timeline of WWII. It’s worth reading and, I liked it. The ending made me think of the sound a phonograph needle would make if you drug it to the right track.</span>

          </span>
