	<tr>
		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Boxall&#39;s 1001  Books You Must Read Before You Die" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/18677166-philip-roth-the-plot-against-america">Boxall&#39;s 1001  Bo...:</a>
