      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/911456-the-plot-against-america">Quotes from The Plot Against ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
